File::Same
==========

File::Same allows you to compare a whole bunch of files (or directories
full of files) for "sameness".

Essentially this was written to detect which files in a multitude
of directories are the same, and allow us to do further processing
on those files.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

Replace make for nmake on Win32.

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Digest::MD5
  File::Spec (included with core perl)

